snippet.title: This is Phantom Panzer for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
You drive around in your armored vehicle shooting tanks. Three different level types, which is nice, and plenty of enemies to shoot. This one is interesting enough to see exactly how long you can survive and keep your base intact. I was relatively pleased to find this one in the wild. 

This may also be referred to as Phantom Tank...


ep112
